The '''Togo paradise whydah''' ('''''Vidua togoensis''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Viduidae]]. It is found in [[Benin]], [[Cameroon]], [[Chad]], [[Ivory Coast]], [[Ghana]], [[Mali]], [[Sierra Leone]], and [[Togo]].

